MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut in the KY11 postcode area of Rosyth. We had no advance warning of this and only became aware of it at 5:08pm. Our engineers have arrived at the Fairykirk Road substation and the team will work to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 8:15pm. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 5:45pm on Monday, 23 November 2020
